{"tid":798671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國第2季GDP成長率上修至4.2%","createTime":"2018-08-29T12:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T03:49:06.000Z","uid":13663,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0330790bf115c82d4d93cd2bf2299bc68d7447","tid":798671,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:46:58.000Z","msg":"美國第2季GDP成長率上修至4.2%<br />\n分享分享留言列印<br />\nA-A+<br />\n2018-08-29 20:45經濟日報 記者鍾詠翔╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部29日表示，第2季國內生產毛額（GDP）成長率從初估的4.1%上修至4.2%，優於經濟學家原估的4%，並寫下2014年第3季以來最大增幅，原因是企業擴大軟體支出，進口減少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987aa090b401260fbd02be5664eb6f046613b4f4","tid":798671,"uid":188396,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c741ce6af3c1640357194736813c7fb45ef4bea","tid":798671,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/29/second-estimate-of-q2-2018-gdp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2Fsecond-estimate-of-q2-2018-gdp.html&d=c%2BU9SroH3bzlC3xuuhKPfHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=394a81d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/29/second-estimate-of-q2-2018-gdp.html</a><br />\n<br />\nBoom! US economy logs best performance in nearly 4 years<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e503abec7ffead97d22fc9cf91bc9bf08558ab","tid":798671,"uid":25424,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"4.2真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor